items.name: Mainstays TV Stand for Flat-Screen TVs up to 42"
items.shortDescription: Elevate a flat screen and store audio and video equipment in modern style with this Mainstays TV Stand for Flat-Screen TVs up to 42". It is constructed of sturdy and durable engineered wood designed for long-lasting use and features a black laminating finish that will blend with many color schemes and decors. This wood TV stand has a profiled top and an enclosed storage area with coordinating hardware on each side that are ideal for storing CDs, DVDs, games, remote controls and more. It also has a center section with two shelves that are ideal for audio and video equipment, game consoles, books, magazines, knick knacks and more. Ideal for a living room, a den or a bedroom, this contemporary black TV stand is ideal for televisions with a width less than 43.1" and a weight of up to 95 lbs. It requires some assembly and includes all of the necessary hardware for added convenience.
